<P><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Sub Layout1_Onload()</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>cboPaginas.additem
"Adobe Systems"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>cboPaginas.additem
"Computer Graphics World"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>cboPaginas.additem
"Epic Games"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>cboPaginas.additem
"Microsoft"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>cboPaginas.additem
"Next Generation"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>cboPaginas.additem
"Sigma"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>cboPaginas.additem
"Visual Basic Brasil"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>End Sub</FONT></FONT></FONT>

<P><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT SIZE=-1>&nbsp; No evento Click do bot&atilde;o
vai o c&oacute;digo da mudan&ccedil;a de p&aacute;gina, que &eacute; controlada
pelo Internet Explorer ou por outro browser com <B>window.location.href</B>,
no caso o Select Case veria o conte&uacute;do do combo e mandaria o usu&aacute;rio
para a p&aacute;gina escolhida:</FONT></FONT>

<P><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Sub cmdOk_Click()</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Select Case
cboPaginas.Text</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Case "Adobe
Systems"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>window.location.href="http://www.adobe.com"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Case "Computer
Graphics World"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>window.location.href="http://www.cgw.com"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Case "Epic Games"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>window.location.href="http://www.epicgames.com"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Case "Microsoft"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>window.location.href="http://www.microsoft.com"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Case "Next Generation"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>window.location.href="http://www.next-generation.com"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Case "Sigma"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>window.location.href="http://www.geocities.com/SiliconValley/Heights/2773/sigma.htm"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>Case "Visual
Basic Brasil"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>window.location.href="http://www.vbbrasil.com"</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>End Select</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><FONT SIZE=-1>End Sub</FONT></FONT></FONT>
<BR>&nbsp;

<P><FONT FACE="Arial"><FONT SIZE=-1>&nbsp; Salve o layout, que ser&aacute;
um arquivo de extens&atilde;o alx. Resta ent&atilde;o colocar uma refer&ecirc;ncia
numa p&aacute;gina html que chame este layout. Abra a p&aacute;gina html
que for usada, deixe o cursosr na posi&ccedil;&atilde;o desejada e v&aacute;
no menu Edit>Insert html layout, o Control Pad ir&aacute; adicionar algumas
